Type: NHHS Photo
Format: BW Glossy Photo
NHHS #: 1999.014.001
Subject: A group of sailors from the USS Saipan led by Chcarp Loren A. Helms, fights across the current with a Mexican family in their boat as they evacuate them from their flooded home in Tampico, Mexico. The group is part of the ""Saipan Flotilla"" which evacuated about 1000 people form the rising flood waters.
